<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf6e81688-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s55115"><num value="55115">§ 55115.</num><heading> Supplies on fish processing vessels</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/usc/t46/s55102">Section 55102 of this title</ref> does not apply to supplies aboard a United States documented fish processing vessel that are necessary and used for processing or assembling fishery products aboard such a vessel.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf6e81689-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/304/s8/c">Pub. L. 109–304, § 8(c)</ref>, <date date="2006-10-06">Oct. 6, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1640">120 Stat. 1640</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
